videos.description: Indiana's Juwan Morgan backs down the Maryland defender and finishes with a bank shot.
videos.headline: Morgan flexes after tough bucket inside

videos.description: Justin Smith comes down the lane and rises up for a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Smith throws down dunk off Hoosiers' inbound pass

videos.description: Maryland C Bruno Fernando comes up with a big block and finishes a dunk to tie the game 37-37.
videos.headline: Fernando rejects shot, throws down dunk

videos.description: Bruno Fernando banks in a 3-pointer from the wing to extend Maryland's lead.
videos.headline: Fernando pumped after banking in 3
